{"word":"G4296 - προκηρύσσω - prokērýssō - prok-ay-rooce'-so - Before preach","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προκηρύσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prokērýssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prok-ay-rooce'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Before preach</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முன்னேகுறி"},{"paragraph":"1. to announce or proclaim by herald beforehand"},{"paragraph":"2. to announce beforehand"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2784 - κηρύσσω - kērýssō - kay-roos'-so/2784\">G2784</a>; to <i>herald</i> (that is, <i>proclaim</i>) <i>in advance:</i> - before (first) preach.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2782/2782\">G2782</a>, <a href=\"#/G2783/2783\">G2783</a>, <a href=\"#/G2784/2784\">G2784</a>, <a href=\"#/G4296/4296\">G4296</a>"}]}